   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Verwandtschaftsweisung für Katharina und Anna, Kinder des Martin Swebel, und Diemut,
               Tochter Katharinas, Witwe des Nikolaus Reblein</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p> 2 Einbr. 4 Zg. (Indez: Item frewnschaft Merten des Swebleins kinder) <rs
                  type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_118">Des nachsten sambcztags nach sand Scolastica tag
                  komen auch fur den rat <rs type="fn" role="witness"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__martin_swebl_StB_I_118">Mertt der Swebel</rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_118_a"><roleName type="title">fraw</roleName>
                        Kathrey, <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__niklas_rebel_StB_I_118"
                              ><add>wittib</add></roleName>
                        <rs type="person" ref="#pe__niklas_rebel_StB_I_118">Niclas <roleName
                              type="dead">seligen </roleName>wittib des Rebleins</rs></rs>, und
                     habent da beweist mit den erbern leuten, mit <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__heinrich_daucher_StB_I_118"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add>
                        </roleName>Hainreichen dem Dawcher</rs>, <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__johann_palwein_QGW_II_I_1353"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add>
                        </roleName>Hannsen dem Paldweyn</rs>, <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__peter_suezzprot_StB_I_6"><roleName type="title"><add>erbern</add>
                        </roleName>Petrein dem Suzzprot</rs> und mit <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__niklas_von_iglau_StB_I_118"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add>
                        </roleName>Niclasen von der Ygla</rs></rs>, das <rs type="fn"
                     role="recipient">des egenanten Mertten des Swebleins zway <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__katharina_StB_I_118_b"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__martin_swebl_StB_I_118">kinder</roleName> Kathrey <roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__konrad_QGW_II_I_1153"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                              chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__peter_QGW_II_I_1153_a"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__diemut_StB_I_118"
                              ><add>rechtew geswistreid chind</add></roleName></rs> und <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__anna_StB_I_118"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__martin_swebl_StB_I_118"><add>kinder</add></roleName>
                           Ann<roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__peter_QGW_II_I_1153_a"><add>rechtew
                              geswistreid chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__konrad_QGW_II_I_1153"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__diemut_StB_I_118"
                              ><add>rechtew geswistreid chind</add></roleName></rs>, die noch nicht
                     vogtper sind</rs>, und <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__diemut_StB_I_118">der egenanten frawn Kathrein <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_118_a">tochter</roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">junkchfraw</roleName> Dyemut<roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__peter_QGW_II_I_1153_a"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__konrad_QGW_II_I_1153"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_118_b"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_118"
                              ><add>rechtew geswistreid chind</add></roleName></rs></rs> mit <rs
                     type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__peter_QGW_II_I_1153_a"><rs
                           type="person" ref="#pe__johann_ledrer_QGW_II_I_1153">Hannsen des <roleName
                              type="prof" cert="unknown">Ledrer</roleName></rs> zwayn <roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_ledrer_QGW_II_I_1153"
                           >chinden</roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_118"><add>chinden</add></roleName>, den got
                           <roleName type="dead">gnad</roleName>, Petrein <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_118_b"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_118"
                              ><add>rechtew geswistreid chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__diemut_StB_I_118"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__konrad_QGW_II_I_1153"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__johann_ledrer_QGW_II_I_1153"
                           ><add>chinden</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_118"><add>chinden</add></roleName><roleName
                           type="dead"><add>gnad</add></roleName>Chunraten<roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__katharina_StB_I_118_b"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_118"
                              ><add>rechtew geswistreid chind</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__diemut_StB_I_118"><add>rechtew geswistreid
                           chind</add></roleName></rs>, die er gehabt hat mit <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_118">seiner andern <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__johann_ledrer_QGW_II_I_1153">hawsfrawn</roleName>
                        Margreten</rs></rs>, rechtew geswistreid chind gewesen sind von vater und
                  von muter. Als darumb die obgenanten erbern leut mit irn trewn an ayde stat vor
                  offem rat habent gesagt, als si ze recht solten.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
